177 A.3d 117 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. TARI D. TURPIN, A/K/A TARID TURPIN, TARI TURRIN AND TARI DEMOND TURPIN, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-408 September Term 2017

079629 December 8, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001745-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
